strings: <voice_0x01001CFA><se_high>Media princess: great work! Champions of the Monster Arena! It's a success!
<voice_0x01001CFB><se_high>Media princess: Your idols are so attractive. The sculptor will surely become your fan!
<voice_0x01001CFC><se_high>Media princess: I know that you have decided to join us on this journey. I am sure he also misses you.
<voice_0x01001CFD><se_high>Media princess: I don't know if he created the demon arena to find someone better than him at fighting demons.
<voice_0x01001D01><se_high>Media princess: I just want to help you if you can break the curse.
<voice_0x01001D02><se_high>Media princess: Thanks for your help this time.
<voice_0x01001CF9><se_high>Can't show up! again!! e804h and event_msg804100
